summary: A player home you can teleport to from anywhere and back again anytime.
descriptionHtml:
Everything works and I am going to leave it as is since I have lost interest in the mod feel free to edit it how you like.
_________________________________________________________________________________________
This mod gives you a spell to teleport to and from your new home from anywhere that you can fast travel from. You can find the Spelltome at Belethor or at Farengar in Whiterun
_________________________________________________________________________________________
A big thank you to DarkenDe for creating the scripting you can find his original mod here http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8261



Dimension Teleport Garden Arena House
author: CappsGrad
